2732
01:27:58,940 --> 01:28:02,660
Daou: Even if it's not you, it's fine.

2733
01:28:02,660 --> 01:28:06,860
Daou: No matter where you are, I won't go looking for you.

2734
01:28:06,860 --> 01:28:11,340
Daou: Ah—ah—ah—ah—ah—ah—won't find you.

2735
