high-pitch showdown still isn't over]

2771
01:29:25,860 --> 01:29:29,300
Manager: Even if it's not you, it's fine.

2772
01:29:29,300 --> 01:29:33,340
Manager: No matter where you are, I won't go looking for you.

2773
01:29:30,660 --> 01:29:33,180
