2782
01:29:51,070 --> 01:29:54,510
Daou: No matter where you are, I won't go looking for you.

2783
01:29:54,710 --> 01:29:56,830
Daou: Ah—ah—ah—ah—ah—ah—

2784
01:29:55,310 --> 01:29:59,070
[Ending with the harmony of Offroad]

2785
01:29:57,150 --> 01:29:59,350
-Offroad: Won't find you.
-Daou: Won't find you.

2786
